join Paciano center
Paciano: Jose, the authorities grow suspicious of educated Filipinos. You must leave quietly.
join Rizal left
Rizal: I understand, brother. But if I remain here, I cannot learn what our country truly needs.
Paciano: Europe will open your eyes, but it will also test you.
Rizal: Then I will face it. Everything I learn there will be for our people.
Paciano: Remember why you are going. Do not forget the Philippines.
Rizal: I will not forget. One day, what I learn will help awaken our nation
leave Rizal
leave Paciano
join Captain center
Captain: Final boarding call. Passengers for Spain must board now.
leave Captain
join Rizal left
Rizal: Farewell, brother. Take care of our family.
join Paciano center
Paciano: Go, Jose. Make our sacrifices worth it.
leave Paciano
leave Rizal
join Captain center
Captain: The seas ahead are long, young man. What brings you to Europe?
join Rizal left
Rizal: Knowledge, Captain. Knowledge that may change my country.
leave Rizal
join passenger center
passenger: Spain is a different world from Manila.
leave passenger
join Rizal left
Rizal: That is why I must see it for myself.